Spellbook: Devolve","product":"Great Cthulhu","tot":"4","img":"/factions/great-cthulhu/unit-mini-deep-one.png","url":"/factions/great-cthulhu?units#_deep-one","keywords":["unit"]},{"name":"Shoggoth","type":"Monster","cost":"2","combat":"2","notes":"Spellbook: Absorb","text":"Cost: 2 Combat: 2
