Spellbook: Regenerate","product":"Great Cthulhu","tot":"2","img":"/factions/great-cthulhu/unit-mini-starspawn.png","url":"/factions/great-cthulhu?units#_starspawn","keywords":["unit"]},{"name":"Cthulhu","type":"Great Old One","cost":"10/4","combat":"6","notes":"How to Awaken Cthulhu:1) There must be a Gate in Great Cthulhu's starting Area (Can be abandoned or enemy-Controlled).2) If this is the first Awakening, pay 10 Power.Otherwise pay 4 Power.3) Cthulhu appears in its starting Area (Remember to gain 1 Elder Sign).Devour (Pre-Battle): The enemy player chooses and Eliminates one of his Monsters or Cultists in the Battle.","text":"Cost: 10/4 Combat: 6
How to Awaken Cthulhu:1) There must be a Gate in Great Cthulhu's starting Area (Can be abandoned or enemy-Controlled).2) If this is the first Awakening, pay 10 Power.Otherwise pay 4 Power.3) Cthulhu appears in its starting Area (Remember to gain 1 Elder Sign).Devour (Pre-Battle): The enemy player chooses and Eliminates one of his Monsters or Cultists in the Battle.","product":"Great Cthulhu","tot":"1","img":"/factions/great-cthulhu/unit-mini-cthulhu.png","url":"/factions/great-cthulhu?units#_cthulhu","keywords":["unit"]},{"name":"Absorb (Pre-Battle)","type":"Spellbook","cost":"Pre-Battle","text":"If a Shoggoth is present, Eliminate one or more of your Monsters or Cultists in the Battle. For each Unit so removed, add 3 dice to the Shoggoth's Combat for that Battle.","product":"Great Cthulhu","img":"/factions/great-cthulhu/icon.png","url":"/factions/great-cthulhu?spellbooks","keywords":["faction-spellbook","spellbook"]},{"name":"Devolve (Ongoing)","type":"Spellbook","cost":"Ongoing","text":"After any player's Action, replace one or more of your Acolyte Cultists anywhere on the Map with Deep Ones from your Pool.","product":"Great Cthulhu","img":"/factions/great-cthulhu/icon.png","url":"/factions/great-cthulhu?spellbooks","keywords":["faction-spellbook","spellbook"]},{"name":"Dreams (Action: Cost 2)","type":"Spellbook","cost":"Action: Cost 2","text":"Choose an Area containing an enemy’s Acolyte Cultist. Your enemy must Eliminate one of his Acolyte Cultists from that Area and replace it with one from your Pool. ","product":"Great Cthulhu","img":"/factions/great-cthulhu/icon.png","url":"/factions/great-cthulhu?spellbooks","keywords":["faction-spellbook","spellbook"]},{"name":"Regenerate (Post-Battle)","type":"Spellbook","cost":"Post-Battle","text":"Assign up to 2 Kill or Pain Battle results to the same Starspawn. If 2 Kills are applied, the Starspawn is Killed. On any other combination of Kill or Pain results, the Starspawn is only Pained.","product":"Great Cthulhu","img":"/factions/great-cthulhu/icon.png","url":"/factions/great-cthulhu?spellbooks","keywords":["faction-spellbook","spellbook"]},{"name":"Submerge (Action: Cost 1)","type":"Spellbook","cost":"Action: Cost 1","text":"If Cthulhu is in an ocean or sea Area, remove him from the Map and place him on your Faction Card, along with any or all of your Units in the Area. Later, as a 0-cost Action, you may place Cthulhu, plus all accompanying Units, into any Area.","product":"Great Cthulhu","img":"/factions/great-cthulhu/icon.png","url":"/factions/great-cthulhu?spellbooks","keywords":["faction-spellbook","spellbook"]},{"name":"Y'ha Nthlei (Ongoing)","type":"Spellbook","cost":"Ongoing","text":"During Gather Power, if Cthulhu is in play, gain 1 Power for each enemy-controlled Gate in an ocean or sea Area.","product":"Great Cthulhu","img":"/factions/great-cthulhu/icon.png","url":"/factions/great-cthulhu?spellbooks","keywords":["faction-spellbook","spellbook"]},{"name":"Black Goat","type":"Faction","product":"Factions","img":"/factions/black-goat/icon.png","url":"/factions/black-goat","keywords":["product","faction"]},{"name":"Acolyte","type":"Cultist","cost":"1","combat":"0","notes":"Combat is 1 with Frenzy Spellbook","text":"Cost: 1 Combat: 0
