How to Awaken Shub-Niggurath:1) You must have a Controlled Gate, and at least 2 Cultists on the Map – they can be in any Area(s).2) Pay 8 Power.3) Remove your 2 Cultists, then place Shub-Niggurath at your Controlled Gate.Combat: Equal to the sum of your Controlled Gates and in-play Cultists. If you have The Red Sign, add another +1 for each Dark Young you have in play.Avatar (Action: Cost 1): Choose an Area and a Faction. Swap the location of Shub-Niggurath with that of a Monster or Cultist in the chosen Area. The owner of the chosen Faction chooses which Unit to relocate.","product":"Black Goat","tot":"1","img":"/factions/black-goat/unit-mini-shub-niggurath.png","url":"/factions/black-goat?units#_shub-niggurath","keywords":["unit"]},{"name":"Blood Sacrifice (Doom Phase)","type":"Spellbook","cost":"Doom Phase","text":"If Shub-Niggurath is in play during the Doom Phase, you can choose to Eliminate one of your Cultists (from anywhere on the map). If you do, gain 1 Elder Sign.","product":"Black Goat","img":"/factions/black-goat/icon.png","url":"/factions/black-goat?spellbooks","keywords":["faction-spellbook","spellbook"]},{"name":"Frenzy (Ongoing)","type":"Spellbook","cost":"Ongoing","text":"Your Cultists now have 1 Combat.","product":"Black Goat","img":"/factions/black-goat/icon.png","url":"/factions/black-goat?spellbooks","keywords":["faction-spellbook","spellbook"]},{"name":"Ghroth (Action: Cost 2)","type":"Spellbook","cost":"Action: Cost 2","text":"Roll a die. If the roll is less than or equal to the number of Areas containing Fungi, your enemies must collectively Eliminate Cultists equal to the die roll. They have 1 minute to decide how to distribute these Eliminations. If time runs out, you choose for them. If the roll is greater than the number of Areas with Fungi, place 1 Acolyte from any Faction’s pool anywhere on the map.","product":"Black Goat","img":"/factions/black-goat/icon.png","url":"/factions/black-goat?spellbooks","keywords":["faction-spellbook","spellbook"]},{"name":"Necrophagy (Post-Battle)","type":"Spellbook","cost":"Post-Battle","text":"Move any or all Ghouls (who did not participate in the Battle) from any Area to the Battle Area, even if your Faction was not involved in the Battle. For each Ghoul so moved, both sides in the Battle suffer an additional Pain result.","product":"Black Goat","img":"/factions/black-goat/icon.png","url":"/factions/black-goat?spellbooks","keywords":["faction-spellbook","spellbook"]},{"name":"The Red Sign (Ongoing)","type":"Spellbook","cost":"Ongoing","text":"Dark Young can Create and Control Gates. Each Dark Young adds 1 to Shub-Niggurath’s Combat and each provides 1 Power during the Gather Power Phase. They do not act as Cultists with respect to any other purpose.","product":"Black Goat","img":"/factions/black-goat/icon.png","url":"/factions/black-goat?spellbooks","keywords":["faction-spellbook","spellbook"]},{"name":"The Thousand Young (Ongoing)","type":"Spellbook","cost":"Ongoing","text":"If Shub-Niggurath is in play, Ghouls, Fungi, and Dark Young cost 1 fewer Power each to Summon.","product":"Black Goat","img":"/factions/black-goat/icon.png","url":"/factions/black-goat?spellbooks","keywords":["faction-spellbook","spellbook"]},{"name":"Bubastis","type":"Faction","product":"Factions","img":"/factions/bubastis/icon.png","url":"/factions/bubastis","keywords":["product","faction"]},{"name":"Earth Cat","type":"Monster","cost":"1","combat":"0","notes":"Special: Generates 1 Power during the Gather Power PhaseSpellbook: Catabolism","text":"Cost: 1 Combat: 0
