Special: Generates 1 Power during the Gather Power PhaseSpellbook: Zagazig","product":"Bubastis","tot":"2","img":"/factions/bubastis/unit-mini-cat-from-mars.png","url":"/factions/bubastis?units#_cat-from-mars","keywords":["unit"]},{"name":"Cat from Saturn","type":"Monster","cost":"3","combat":"2","notes":"Special: Generates 1 Power during the Gather Power PhaseSpellbook: Savagery","text":"Cost: 3 Combat: 2
