How to Awaken Bastet:1) All your Cat varieties are in play.2) Pay 6 Power.3) Place Bastet in an Area containing no enemy Units.Combat: Add 1 Kill to your combat total (Bastet rolls no dice); the enemy must lower their Kill total by 1.Requires Attention (Doom Phase): During the Doom Phase, if Bastet is in an Area containing an enemy Cultist, you may perform a Ritual of Annihilation. For you, this adds exactly 4 Doom plus:  If Bastet's Area has an Enemy-Controlled Gate, gain 1 Elder Sign If Bastet's Area has an Enemy Great Old One, gain 2 Elder SignThese rewards are additive.","product":"Bubastis","tot":"1","img":"/factions/bubastis/unit-mini-bastet.png","url":"/factions/bubastis?units#_bastet","keywords":["unit"]},{"name":"Predator (Post-Battle)","type":"Spellbook","cost":"Post-Battle","text":"If a Cat from Uranus was in the Battle, you can select one Unit lost by the enemy. He must eliminate a second Unit of that type anywhere on the Map, if possible.","product":"Bubastis","img":"/factions/bubastis/icon.png","url":"/factions/bubastis?spellbooks","keywords":["faction-spellbook","spellbook"]},{"name":"Zagazig (Pre-Battle)","type":"Spellbook","cost":"Pre-Battle","text":"If a Cat from Mars is in the Battle, all rolled Pains become Kills, and all rolled Kills become Pains.","product":"Bubastis","img":"/factions/bubastis/icon.png","url":"/factions/bubastis?spellbooks","keywords":["faction-spellbook","spellbook"]},{"name":"Catabolism (Ongoing)","type":"Spellbook","cost":"Ongoing","text":"Earth Cats can Recruit monsters, as if the monsters were cultists, instead of needing to Summon them.","product":"Bubastis","img":"/factions/bubastis/icon.png","url":"/factions/bubastis?spellbooks","keywords":["faction-spellbook","spellbook"]},{"name":"Catnapping (Action: Cost 1)","type":"Spellbook","cost":"Action: Cost 1","text":"Choose any or all enemy Factions in Bastet’s Area. Move all Units belonging to those Faction(s) from that Area to the Moon. When an enemy Unit on the Moon leaves, you gain the Power they spend on movement.","product":"Bubastis","img":"/factions/bubastis/icon.png","url":"/factions/bubastis?spellbooks","keywords":["faction-spellbook","spellbook"]},{"name":"Savagery (Pre-Battle)","type":"Spellbook","cost":"Pre-Battle","text":"Pay 1 Power to increase the Combat of all Cats from Saturn by 4 for this Battle.","product":"Bubastis","img":"/factions/bubastis/icon.png","url":"/factions/bubastis?spellbooks","keywords":["faction-spellbook","spellbook"]},{"name":"Ailurophobia (Doom Phase)","type":"Spellbook","cost":"Doom Phase","text":"Gain 1 Doom per Monster Cat Variety sharing any non-Moon Area with Unit(s) from enemy Factions.","product":"Bubastis","img":"/factions/bubastis/icon.png","url":"/factions/bubastis?spellbooks","keywords":["faction-spellbook","spellbook"]},{"name":"Crawling Chaos","type":"Faction","product":"Factions","img":"/factions/crawling-chaos/icon.png","url":"/factions/crawling-chaos","keywords":["product","faction"]},{"name":"Acolyte","type":"Cultist","cost":"1","combat":"0","notes":"","text":"Cost: 1 Combat: 0
