Spellbook: Invisibility","product":"Crawling Chaos","tot":"3","img":"/factions/crawling-chaos/unit-mini-flying-polyp.png","url":"/factions/crawling-chaos?units#_flying-polyp","keywords":["unit"]},{"name":"Hunting Horror","type":"Monster","cost":"3","combat":"2","notes":"Spellbook: Seek and Destroy","text":"Cost: 3 Combat: 2
