How to Awaken Nyarlathotep:1) You must have a Controlled Gate.2) Pay 10 Power. Nyarlathotep appears at the controlled Gate.Combat: Equals the total of your own Faction Spellbooks plus the Faction Spellbooks of your opponent in the Battle.The Harbinger (Post-Battle): If Nyarlathotep is in a Battle in which one or more enemy Great Old Ones are Pained or Killed, you receive Power equal to half the cost to Awaken those Great Old Ones. Per enemy Great Old One, you may choose to receive 2 Elder Signs instead of Power. Harbringer takes effect even if Nyarlathotep is Killed or Pained in the Battle himself. ","product":"Crawling Chaos","tot":"1","img":"/factions/crawling-chaos/unit-mini-nyarlathotep.png","url":"/factions/crawling-chaos?units#_nyarlathotep","keywords":["unit"]},{"name":"Abduct (Pre-Battle)","type":"Spellbook","cost":"Pre-Battle","text":"Eliminate one or more Nightgaunts from the Battle. For each one Eliminated, your enemy must Eliminate one of his own Monsters or Cultists from the Battle.","product":"Crawling Chaos","img":"/factions/crawling-chaos/icon.png","url":"/factions/crawling-chaos?spellbooks","keywords":["faction-spellbook","spellbook"]},{"name":"Invisibility (Pre-Battle)","type":"Spellbook","cost":"Pre-Battle","text":"Select one Monster or Cultist (from either Faction) for each Flying Polyp present and \"exempt\" it. The selected Unit does not participate in the rest of the Battle.","product":"Crawling Chaos","img":"/factions/crawling-chaos/icon.png","url":"/factions/crawling-chaos?spellbooks","keywords":["faction-spellbook","spellbook"]},{"name":"Seek and Destroy  (Pre-Battle)","type":"Spellbook","cost":"Pre-Battle","text":"Immediately move any or all Hunting Horrors from any Area to the Battle Area.","product":"Crawling Chaos","img":"/factions/crawling-chaos/icon.png","url":"/factions/crawling-chaos?spellbooks","keywords":["faction-spellbook","spellbook"]},{"name":"Emissary of the Outer Gods (Post-Battle)","type":"Spellbook","cost":"Post-Battle","text":"Unless an enemy Great Old One is involved in the Battle, a Kill applied to Nyarlathotep becomes a Pain. If Nyarlathotep cannot be Pained due to being surrounded, he is not Eliminated.","product":"Crawling Chaos","img":"/factions/crawling-chaos/icon.png","url":"/factions/crawling-chaos?spellbooks","keywords":["faction-spellbook","spellbook"]},{"name":"The Thousand Forms (Action: Cost 0)","type":"Spellbook","cost":"Action: Cost 0","text":"If Nyarlathotep is in play, roll 1d6. Your foes lose that much Power between them; they have 1 minute to decide how much each loses. If they cannot agree, you get the rolled number as Power added to your total. Flip this spellbook face-down to indicate it cannot be used again this Action Phase. During Gather Power, flip it face-up again.","product":"Crawling Chaos","img":"/factions/crawling-chaos/icon.png","url":"/factions/crawling-chaos?spellbooks","keywords":["faction-spellbook","spellbook"]},{"name":"Madness (Post-Battle)","type":"Spellbook","cost":"Post-Battle","text":"After all Pain results have been assigned, you, rather than the Units' owners, choose the Area(s) to which all Pained Units will go. You may apply these results in any order (rather than the normal 'attacker first, then defender'), but you must still follow all other rules. Do this even for Battles in which you did not participate.","product":"Crawling Chaos","img":"/factions/crawling-chaos/icon.png","url":"/factions/crawling-chaos?spellbooks","keywords":["faction-spellbook","spellbook"]},{"name":"Daemon Sultan","type":"Faction","product":"Factions","img":"/factions/daemon-sultan/icon.png","url":"/factions/daemon-sultan","keywords":["product","faction"]},{"name":"Acolyte","type":"Cultist","cost":"1","combat":"0","notes":"","text":"Cost: 1 Combat: 0
","product":"Daemon Sultan","tot":"6","img":"/factions/daemon-sultan/unit-mini-acolyte.png","url":"/factions/daemon-sultan?units#_acolyte","keywords":["unit"]},{"name":"Larva Thesis","type":"Monster","cost":"1","combat":"0","notes":"Combat is 2 if Avatar Thesis is in play","text":"Cost: 1 Combat: 0
Combat is 2 if Avatar Thesis is in play","product":"Daemon Sultan","tot":"2","img":"/factions/daemon-sultan/unit-mini-larva-thesis.png","url":"/factions/daemon-sultan?units#_larva-thesis","keywords":["unit"]},{"name":"Larva Antithesis","type":"Monster","cost":"1","combat":"0","notes":"Combat is 2 if Avatar Antithesis is in play","text":"Cost: 1 Combat: 0
