The Chaos Gates can only be occupied by Daemon a Sultan Acolyte. Otherwise it is like a normal Gate except it can only be placed via the Chaos Gate Spellbook. During the Doom Phase, an Abandoned Chaos Gate is exchanged for a normal Gate.Spellbooks: Chaos Gate, Animate Matter, Traitors","product":"Daemon Sultan","tot":"3","img":"/factions/daemon-sultan/unit-mini-chaos-gate.png","url":"/factions/daemon-sultan?units#_chaos-gate","keywords":["unit"]},{"name":"Avatar Thesis","type":"Great Old One","cost":"?","combat":"?","notes":"How to Awaken Avatar Thesis:1) Set the Azathoth marker on the Doom track on any desired spot from 0 to 8.2) Pay Power equal to the Azathoth marker's setting.3) Each other player gains 1 Power OR choose an enemy player to gain 2 Power.Combat: Equals the Azathoth marker's position.Spellbook: Undirected Energy","text":"Cost: ? Combat: ?
How to Awaken Avatar Thesis:1) Set the Azathoth marker on the Doom track on any desired spot from 0 to 8.2) Pay Power equal to the Azathoth marker's setting.3) Each other player gains 1 Power OR choose an enemy player to gain 2 Power.Combat: Equals the Azathoth marker's position.Spellbook: Undirected Energy","product":"Daemon Sultan","tot":"1","img":"/factions/daemon-sultan/unit-mini-avatar-thesis.png","url":"/factions/daemon-sultan?units#_avatar-thesis","keywords":["unit"]},{"name":"Avatar Antithesis","type":"Great Old One","cost":"?","combat":"?","notes":"How to Awaken Avatar Antithesis:1) Avatar Thesis must have been Awakened (it need not be in play).2) Pay Power equal to 8 minus the Azathoth marker's setting.3) Each other player gains 1 Doom OR choose an enemy player who gains an Elder Sign.Combat: Equals 8 minus the Azathoth marker's position.Spellbook: Fiendish Growth","text":"Cost: ? Combat: ?
