How to Awaken Avatar Synthesis:1) Both Avatar Thesis and Antithesis must have been Awakened (they need not be in play).2) Pay 8 Power.3) Roll the Azathoth die. All enemies have 2 minutes to decide how to collectively lose that much Power and/or Doom, if they cannot agree then you win the game. In a 2-3 player game halve the die roll result (rounded up).Combat: First roll the Azathoth die, then roll that many combat dice.Cosmic Ruler (Post-Battle): When any Avatar is choosen to recieve a Kill or Elimination, instead you can Eliminate another Avatar in its stead, from anywhere on the map.","product":"Daemon Sultan","tot":"1","img":"/factions/daemon-sultan/unit-mini-avatar-synthesis.png","url":"/factions/daemon-sultan?units#_avatar-synthesis","keywords":["unit"]},{"name":"Animate Matter (Action: Cost 1)","type":"Spellbook","cost":"Action: Cost 1","text":"Flip this Spellbook face down. Move a controlled Chaos Gate from its Area to an adjacent Area, taking its Cultist along. You cannot move the Gate to another player’s Start Area. If the new Area has an existing physical Gate, replace that Gate with the Chaos Gate.","product":"Daemon Sultan","img":"/factions/daemon-sultan/icon.png","url":"/factions/daemon-sultan?spellbooks","keywords":["faction-spellbook","spellbook"]},{"name":"Chaos Gate (Action: Cost 1)","type":"Spellbook","cost":"Action: Cost 1","text":"Flip this Spellbook face down, then place a Chaos Gate in any area without a Gate.","product":"Daemon Sultan","img":"/factions/daemon-sultan/icon.png","url":"/factions/daemon-sultan?spellbooks","keywords":["faction-spellbook","spellbook"]},{"name":"Consummation (Action: Cost 1)","type":"Spellbook","cost":"Action: Cost 1","text":"Flip this spellbook face-down. Then flip one of your face-down faction spellbooks face-up again, permitting its re-use this turn.","product":"Daemon Sultan","img":"/factions/daemon-sultan/icon.png","url":"/factions/daemon-sultan?spellbooks","keywords":["faction-spellbook","spellbook"]},{"name":"Fiendish Growth (Action: Cost 1)","type":"Spellbook","cost":"Action: Cost 1","text":"Flip this spellbook face down if Avatar Antithesis is in play. Place 1 free Monster or Acolyte from your pool in Avatar Antithesis' Area per Faction with Units in that Area, including yours.","product":"Daemon Sultan","img":"/factions/daemon-sultan/icon.png","url":"/factions/daemon-sultan?spellbooks","keywords":["faction-spellbook","spellbook"]},{"name":"Traitors! (Action: Cost 1)","type":"Spellbook","cost":"Action: Cost 1","text":"Flip this Spellbook face down. Replace your controlled Chaos Gate with a Normal Gate, and replace its Controlling Cultist with another player's Cultist from his Pool. Your cultist returns to your Pool. If you have no other Units in the Area, gain an Elder Sign.","product":"Daemon Sultan","img":"/factions/daemon-sultan/icon.png","url":"/factions/daemon-sultan?spellbooks","keywords":["faction-spellbook","spellbook"]},{"name":"Undirected Energy (Action: Cost 1)","type":"Spellbook","cost":"Action: Cost 1","text":"Flip this spellbook face-down if Avatar Thesis is in play. Gain 1 Power per faction with units in Thesis’s area, including you.","product":"Daemon Sultan","img":"/factions/daemon-sultan/icon.png","url":"/factions/daemon-sultan?spellbooks","keywords":["faction-spellbook","spellbook"]},{"name":"Opener of the Way","type":"Faction","product":"Factions","img":"/factions/opener-of-the-way/icon.png","url":"/factions/opener-of-the-way","keywords":["product","faction"]},{"name":"Acolyte","type":"Cultist","cost":"1","combat":"0","notes":"Spellbook: The Million Favored Ones","text":"Cost: 1 Combat: 0
