How to Awaken Tsathoggua1) You must have a Formless Spawn on the map.2) Pay 8 Power. Place Tsathoggua in the Area with the Formless Spawn.Combat: Equals the opponent's current Power or 2, whichever is greater.Lethargy (Action: Cost 0): If Tsathoggua is in play, do nothing. This counts as an Action.","product":"Sleeper","tot":"1","img":"/factions/sleeper/unit-mini-tsathoggua.png","url":"/factions/sleeper?units#_tsathoggua","keywords":["unit"]},{"name":"Ancient Sorcery (Action: Cost 1)","type":"Spellbook","cost":"Action: Cost 1","text":"Remove a Serpent Man from the Map and place him on an enemy's Faction Card. You now have access to that Faction's Unique Ability until the end of the next Doom Phase. At that point, gain 1 Power and replace the Serpent Man anywhere on the Map. If a Faction's Unique Ability mentions a Great Old One, it is also considered to include Tsathoggua.","product":"Sleeper","img":"/factions/sleeper/icon.png","url":"/factions/sleeper?spellbooks","keywords":["faction-spellbook","spellbook"]},{"name":"Burrow (Ongoing)","type":"Spellbook","cost":"Ongoing","text":"After a Move Action in which you spend 2 or more Power moving Units, regain 1 Power.","product":"Sleeper","img":"/factions/sleeper/icon.png","url":"/factions/sleeper?spellbooks","keywords":["faction-spellbook","spellbook"]},{"name":"Capture Monster (Action: Cost 1)","type":"Spellbook","cost":"Action: Cost 1","text":"Tsathoggua can Capture Enemy Monsters in the same manner as Cultists are Captured. They are sacrificed for 1 Power in the next Gather Power Phase.","product":"Sleeper","img":"/factions/sleeper/icon.png","url":"/factions/sleeper?spellbooks","keywords":["faction-spellbook","spellbook"]},{"name":"Cursed Slumber (Action: Cost 1)","type":"Spellbook","cost":"Action: Cost 1","text":"Remove your Controlled Gate and its Cultist from the map and place it on your Faction Card. This Gate and Cultist still provide Power and Doom points, but are immune to enemy abilities. As a Cost 1 Action, return the Gate and Cultist to any Area lacking a Gate. You may only have one Gate on your Faction Card at a time.","product":"Sleeper","img":"/factions/sleeper/icon.png","url":"/factions/sleeper?spellbooks","keywords":["faction-spellbook","spellbook"]},{"name":"Demand Sacrifice (Pre-Battle)","type":"Spellbook","cost":"Pre-Battle","text":"If Tsathoggua is in play, your enemy chooses ONE of the following options before a Battle with you:1) You gain an Elder Sign.OR2) All of their Kill results against your Units in this Battle count as Pains instead.","product":"Sleeper","img":"/factions/sleeper/icon.png","url":"/factions/sleeper?spellbooks","keywords":["faction-spellbook","spellbook"]},{"name":"Energy Nexus (Ongoing)","type":"Spellbook","cost":"Ongoing","text":"Just before a Battle in an Area containing a Wizard, you may take one Action that originates in the Area for its normal Power cost. The Battle proceeds once that Action is finished, starting with Pre- Battle Spellbooks and abilities.","product":"Sleeper","img":"/factions/sleeper/icon.png","url":"/factions/sleeper?spellbooks","keywords":["faction-spellbook","spellbook"]},{"name":"Tcho-Tcho","type":"Faction","product":"Factions","img":"/factions/tcho-tcho/icon.png","url":"/factions/tcho-tcho","keywords":["product","faction"]},{"name":"Acolyte","type":"Cultist","cost":"1","combat":"0","notes":"Spellbook: Soulless","text":"Cost: 1 Combat: 0
