How to Awaken Ubbo-Sathla:1) You have a controlled Gate and a High Priest in play (he need not be with the Gate) during the Doom phase or the Action phase.2) If it is the Doom phase, pay 0 Power; if it is the Action phase, pay 6 Power.3) Eliminate the High Priest, then place Ubbo-Sathla at your controlled Gate.Combat: Equals to Growth counter on the Doom track.Hell's Banquet (Doom phase): Once Ubbo-Sathla has been Awakened, starting with the following Doom phase, and whether or not Ubbo-Sathla is still in play, roll 1d6 and increase its Growth counter by the die roll.","product":"Tcho-Tcho","tot":"1","img":"/factions/tcho-tcho/unit-mini-ubbo-sathla.png","url":"/factions/tcho-tcho?units#_ubbo-sathla","keywords":["unit"]},{"name":"Hierophants (Ongoing)","type":"Spellbook","cost":"Ongoing","text":"When you earn a Faction Spellbook (including this one), place a High Priest at one of your Gates. If there are no High Priests in your Pool, instead advance Ubbo-Sathla’s Growth counter by 1. When this Spellbook is first taken, if you are using the High Priests expansion, then all Factions place a High Priest at one of their Gates.","product":"Tcho-Tcho","img":"/factions/tcho-tcho/icon.png","url":"/factions/tcho-tcho?spellbooks","keywords":["faction-spellbook","spellbook"]},{"name":"Soulless (Ongoing)","type":"Spellbook","cost":"Ongoing","text":"When Captured and Sacrificed, your Cultists provide 0 Power (instead of the normal 1 Power).","product":"Tcho-Tcho","img":"/factions/tcho-tcho/icon.png","url":"/factions/tcho-tcho?spellbooks","keywords":["faction-spellbook","spellbook"]},{"name":"Terror (Battle)","type":"Spellbook","cost":"Battle","text":"Choose one:1) Your enemy’s Combat total is reduced by 1 per Proto-Shoggoth in the Battle.2) Your Combat total is increased by 1 per Proto-Shoggoth in the Battle.","product":"Tcho-Tcho","img":"/factions/tcho-tcho/icon.png","url":"/factions/tcho-tcho?spellbooks","keywords":["faction-spellbook","spellbook"]},{"name":"Idolatry (Action: Cost 1)","type":"Spellbook","cost":"Action: Cost 1","text":"Select an Area containing another Faction’s starting Glyph (even if that Faction is not in play). Move any or all of your Units in adjacent Areas into the selected Area.","product":"Tcho-Tcho","img":"/factions/tcho-tcho/icon.png","url":"/factions/tcho-tcho?spellbooks","keywords":["faction-spellbook","spellbook"]},{"name":"Martyrdom (Post-Battle)","type":"Spellbook","cost":"Post-Battle","text":"If your High Priest is Killed, all Kills assigned to your other Units become Pains instead.","product":"Tcho-Tcho","img":"/factions/tcho-tcho/icon.png","url":"/factions/tcho-tcho?spellbooks","keywords":["faction-spellbook","spellbook"]},{"name":"Tablets of the Gods (Doom Phase)","type":"Spellbook","cost":"Doom Phase","text":"When you perform a Ritual of Annihilation, you also receive 1 additional Elder Sign for each Gate at which you have any High Priests. Then, Eliminate all your High Priests. This is not optional.","product":"Tcho-Tcho","img":"/factions/tcho-tcho/icon.png","url":"/factions/tcho-tcho?spellbooks","keywords":["faction-spellbook","spellbook"]},{"name":"Dark Rituals (Action: Cost 0)","type":"Spellbook","cost":"Action: Cost 0","text":"Flip this spellbook face down. All Factions with your High Priest(s) in their Start Areas must pay you 2 Power or 2 Doom (their choice). A Faction with less than 2 Power or Doom is immune. Flip this Spellbook face up again at the Doom Phase.","product":"Tcho-Tcho","img":"/factions/tcho-tcho/icon.png","url":"/factions/tcho-tcho?spellbooks","keywords":["faction-spellbook","spellbook"]},{"name":"Fulmination (Post-Battle)","type":"Spellbook","cost":"Post-Battle","text":"If Ubbo-Sathla is Killed in a Battle, you may remove it from the game permanently, and gain 1 Elder Sign for each Unit Killed (by either side) in that Battle.","product":"Tcho-Tcho","img":"/factions/tcho-tcho/icon.png","url":"/factions/tcho-tcho?spellbooks","keywords":["faction-spellbook","spellbook"]},{"name":"Surprise! (Action: Cost 2)","type":"Spellbook","cost":"Action: Cost 2","text":"Choose an enemy Faction. That player selects and Eliminates one of their Acolytes; Replace it with a Proto-Shoggoth from your Pool.","product":"Tcho-Tcho","img":"/factions/tcho-tcho/icon.png","url":"/factions/tcho-tcho?spellbooks","keywords":["faction-spellbook","spellbook"]},{"name":"Doomsday (Once Only)","type":"Spellbook","cost":"Once Only","text":"If you have a Controlled Gate, flip this card face down, then immediately take from the Pool one Independent Great Old One with a cost of exactly 2 or 4 and place it at that Gate. Take its Loyalty Card.","product":"Tcho-Tcho","img":"/factions/tcho-tcho/icon.png","url":"/factions/tcho-tcho?spellbooks","keywords":["faction-spellbook","spellbook"]},{"name":"Inerrant (Doom Phase)","type":"Spellbook","cost":"Doom Phase","text":"When you perform a Ritual of Annihilation, gain 1 additional Elder Sign for each enemy-Controlled Gate at which you have any Great Old Ones.","product":"Tcho-Tcho","img":"/factions/tcho-tcho/icon.png","url":"/factions/tcho-tcho?spellbooks","keywords":["faction-spellbook","spellbook"]},{"name":"Otherworld Alliances (Ongoing)","type":"Spellbook","cost":"Ongoing","text":"Your Neutral Monsters and Terrors have +1 Combat.","product":"Tcho-Tcho","img":"/factions/tcho-tcho/icon.png","url":"/factions/tcho-tcho?spellbooks","keywords":["faction-spellbook","spellbook"]},{"name":"The Ancients","type":"Faction","product":"Factions","img":"/factions/the-ancients/icon.png","url":"/factions/the-ancients","keywords":["product","faction"]},{"name":"Acolyte","type":"Cultist","cost":"1","combat":"0","notes":"","text":"Cost: 1 Combat: 0
