You may use the Create Gate Action to Create Cathedrals instead of Gates.Spellbooks, Worship Services, Consecration, Unholy GroundSpecial: If all 4 Cathedrals are in play, you may Awaken an Independent Great Old One without your own Great Old One (when Awakening Cthugha this way, just pay 6 Power).","product":"The Ancients","tot":"4","img":"/factions/the-ancients/unit-mini-cathedral.png","url":"/factions/the-ancients?units#_cathedral","keywords":["unit"]},{"name":"Brainless (Ongoing)","type":"Spellbook","cost":"Ongoing","text":"Reanimated now cost 1 Power to Summon. They may only Move, Capture, or declare Battle if they share an Area with one or more of your non- Reanimated Units. This is not optional.","product":"The Ancients","img":"/factions/the-ancients/icon.png","url":"/factions/the-ancients?spellbooks","keywords":["faction-spellbook","spellbook"]},{"name":"Consecration (Doom Phase)","type":"Spellbook","cost":"Doom Phase","text":"When you perform a Ritual of Annihilation, gain 1 Elder Sign if at least one Cathedral is in play. If all four Cathedrals are in play, gain 2 Elder Signs instead.","product":"The Ancients","img":"/factions/the-ancients/icon.png","url":"/factions/the-ancients?spellbooks","keywords":["faction-spellbook","spellbook"]},{"name":"Extinction (Ongoing)","type":"Spellbook","cost":"Ongoing","text":"Yothans now cost 3 Power to Summon. When a Yothan is Killed or Eliminated, remove it permanently from the game. This is not optional.","product":"The Ancients","img":"/factions/the-ancients/icon.png","url":"/factions/the-ancients?spellbooks","keywords":["faction-spellbook","spellbook"]},{"name":"Festival (Ongoing)","type":"Spellbook","cost":"Ongoing","text":"Un-Men now cost 0 Power to Summon. When you Summon an Un-Man, also select an enemy to gain 1 Power.  This is not optional.","product":"The Ancients","img":"/factions/the-ancients/icon.png","url":"/factions/the-ancients?spellbooks","keywords":["faction-spellbook","spellbook"]},{"name":"Unholy Ground (Post-Battle)","type":"Spellbook","cost":"Post-Battle","text":"If there is a Cathedral in the Battle Area, you may choose to remove a Cathedral from anywhere. If you do, an enemy Great Old One in the Battle must be Eliminated by its owner.","product":"The Ancients","img":"/factions/the-ancients/icon.png","url":"/factions/the-ancients?spellbooks","keywords":["faction-spellbook","spellbook"]},{"name":"Worship Services (Gather Power Phase)","type":"Spellbook","cost":"Gather Power Phase","text":"Gain 1 Power for each Cathedral that shares an Area with an enemy Gate. Those enemies each gain 1 Power.","product":"The Ancients","img":"/factions/the-ancients/icon.png","url":"/factions/the-ancients?spellbooks","keywords":["faction-spellbook","spellbook"]},{"name":"The Invasion","type":"Faction","product":"Factions","img":"/factions/the-invasion/icon.png","url":"/factions/the-invasion","keywords":["product","faction"]},{"name":"Demon Larvae","type":"Cultist","cost":"1","combat":"0","notes":"Portend (Action: Cost X): In an Area containing Demon Larvae and a Portent, add another Portent. If there are 4 Portents in the Area remove them and put a Lord's Shadowand a Fiend in the Area. Cost equals the number of Portents already in the Area plus one (2/3/4) OR 0 if the number of your Larvae in the Areais equal to or greater than the number of the Portents already in the Area plus one.Larvae (ongoing): Your Larvae cannot Build or Control Gates but count as Acolytes for all other purposes. This is not optional.","text":"Cost: 1 Combat: 0
Portend (Action: Cost X): In an Area containing Demon Larvae and a Portent, add another Portent. If there are 4 Portents in the Area remove them and put a Lord's Shadowand a Fiend in the Area. Cost equals the number of Portents already in the Area plus one (2/3/4) OR 0 if the number of your Larvae in the Areais equal to or greater than the number of the Portents already in the Area plus one.Larvae (ongoing): Your Larvae cannot Build or Control Gates but count as Acolytes for all other purposes. This is not optional.","product":"The Invasion","tot":"6","img":"/factions/the-invasion/unit-mini-demon-larvae.png","url":"/factions/the-invasion?units#_demon-larvae","keywords":["unit"]},{"name":"Gryllus","type":"Monster","cost":"2","combat":"1","notes":"Spellbook: Scavenge","text":"Cost: 2 Combat: 1
Spellbook: Scavenge","product":"The Invasion","tot":"6","img":"/factions/the-invasion/unit-mini-gryllus.png","url":"/factions/the-invasion?units#_gryllus","keywords":["unit"]},{"name":"Fiend","type":"Monster","cost":"4","combat":"3","notes":"Spellbook: Entropy Siphon","text":"Cost: 4 Combat: 3
Spellbook: Entropy Siphon","product":"The Invasion","tot":"4","img":"/factions/the-invasion/unit-mini-fiend.png","url":"/factions/the-invasion?units#_fiend","keywords":["unit"]},{"name":"Baphomet","type":"Great Old One","cost":"0","combat":"?","notes":"How to Awaken Baphomet1) Permanently remove your Faction Unit in an Area from the game.2) Baphomet appears in that Area.Combat: Equal to 4 + the total amount of Doom you've earned from Elder Signs this Action Phase.Unquenchable Thirst (Ongoing): Pay 1 Doom (instead of Power) to Attack or Capture in Baphomet's Area. This is not optional and cannot be disabled or removed by other effects.Sacrament of Flesh (Doom Phase): If Baphomet is in play, you must:1) Permanently remove a non-token Unit you Control from the game (or 2 Units if you have all 6 Spellbooks). Spare 1 Unit for each Cultist that was on your Faction Card during Gather Power. 2) Gain an Elder Sign (or 2 if you have all 6 Spellbooks).","text":"Cost: 0 Combat: ?
How to Awaken Baphomet1) Permanently remove your Faction Unit in an Area from the game.2) Baphomet appears in that Area.Combat: Equal to 4 + the total amount of Doom you've earned from Elder Signs this Action Phase.Unquenchable Thirst (Ongoing): Pay 1 Doom (instead of Power) to Attack or Capture in Baphomet's Area. This is not optional and cannot be disabled or removed by other effects.Sacrament of Flesh (Doom Phase): If Baphomet is in play, you must:1) Permanently remove a non-token Unit you Control from the game (or 2 Units if you have all 6 Spellbooks). Spare 1 Unit for each Cultist that was on your Faction Card during Gather Power. 2) Gain an Elder Sign (or 2 if you have all 6 Spellbooks).","product":"The Invasion","tot":"1","img":"/factions/the-invasion/unit-mini-baphomet.png","url":"/factions/the-invasion?units#_baphomet","keywords":["unit"]},{"name":"Infernolatreia (Ongoing)","type":"Spellbook","cost":"Ongoing","text":"If you would gain 1 or more Elder Signs, you may instead first draw and look at Elder Signs equal to the number of your Lord's Shadows plus one. Keep the gained amount and return the rest (if any).","product":"The Invasion","img":"/factions/the-invasion/icon.png","url":"/factions/the-invasion?spellbooks","keywords":["faction-spellbook","spellbook"]},{"name":"Eclipse (Only Once)","type":"Spellbook","cost":"Only Once","text":" Play this at any time prior to the Doom Phase. All other Factions (except Sleeper, if copying Eternal Servitude) do not gain Doom for Unit-Controlled Gates this Doom Phase. They may still earn Doom from Rituals and other effects, if able. Flip this Spellbook face down after use to indicate it cannot be used again.","product":"The Invasion","img":"/factions/the-invasion/icon.png","url":"/factions/the-invasion?spellbooks","keywords":["faction-spellbook","spellbook"]},{"name":"Scavenge (Action: Cost 2)","type":"Spellbook","cost":"Action: Cost 2","text":"Move any number of your Grylluses. Then, as part of the same Action, all of your Grylluses may either Attack or Capture in their Area(s) for free (but not more than one Battle per Area). Only your Grylluses participate on your side of the Battle.","product":"The Invasion","img":"/factions/the-invasion/icon.png","url":"/factions/the-invasion?spellbooks","keywords":["faction-spellbook","spellbook"]},{"name":"Blood Offering (Action: Cost 0)","type":"Spellbook","cost":"Action: Cost 0","text":"Draw and reveal 4 Elder Signs. Enemies have 2 minutes to offer you a Cultist from play in exchange for the Doom from a single revealed Elder Sign. You may accept one offer and Capture that Cultist; that player gains Doom for that Elder Sign, which is discarded. Return all remaining Elder Signs to the pool. Flip this face down until the Gather Power Phase.","product":"The Invasion","img":"/factions/the-invasion/icon.png","url":"/factions/the-invasion?spellbooks","keywords":["faction-spellbook","spellbook"]},{"name":"Hellgate (Action: Cost 2)","type":"Spellbook","cost":"Action: Cost 2","text":"Relocate any number of your Units from a single Area with a Lord's Shadow to another single Area with a Lord's Shadow.","product":"The Invasion","img":"/factions/the-invasion/icon.png","url":"/factions/the-invasion?spellbooks","keywords":["faction-spellbook","spellbook"]},{"name":"Entropy Siphon (Ongoing)","type":"Spellbook","cost":"Ongoing","text":"Fiends can Control Gates. At the end of the Doom Phase, enemies must collectively decide how to lose 4 power for each Fiend-Controlled Gate. For every 4 power not lost this way, all players with more Doom than you lose 1 Doom.","product":"The Invasion","img":"/factions/the-invasion/icon.png","url":"/factions/the-invasion?spellbooks","keywords":["faction-spellbook","spellbook"]},{"name":"Yellow Sign","type":"Faction","product":"Factions","img":"/factions/yellow-sign/icon.png","url":"/factions/yellow-sign","keywords":["product","faction"]},{"name":"Acolyte","type":"Cultist","cost":"1","combat":"0","notes":"Spellbook: Passion","text":"Cost: 1 Combat: 0
Spellbook: Passion","product":"Yellow Sign","tot":"6","img":"/factions/yellow-sign/unit-mini-acolyte.png","url":"/factions/yellow-sign?units#_acolyte","keywords":["unit"]},{"name":"Undead","type":"Monster","cost":"1","combat":"?","notes":"Combat: Roll 1 die less than the total Undead in the area. (i.e. 4 undead roll 3 dice in all)Spellbook: Zingaya","text":"Cost: 1 Combat: ?
Combat: Roll 1 die less than the total Undead in the area. (i.e. 4 undead roll 3 dice in all)Spellbook: Zingaya","product":"Yellow Sign","tot":"6","img":"/factions/yellow-sign/unit-mini-undead.png","url":"/factions/yellow-sign?units#_undead","keywords":["unit"]},{"name":"Byakhee","type":"Monster","cost":"2","combat":"?","notes":"Combat: Roll 1 die more than the total Byakhee in the area. (i.e. 4 Byakhee roll 5 dice in all)Spellbook: Shriek of the Byakhee","text":"Cost: 2 Combat: ?
Combat: Roll 1 die more than the total Byakhee in the area. (i.e. 4 Byakhee roll 5 dice in all)Spellbook: Shriek of the Byakhee","product":"Yellow Sign","tot":"4","img":"/factions/yellow-sign/unit-mini-byakhee.png","url":"/factions/yellow-sign?units#_byakhee","keywords":["unit"]},{"name":"King In Yellow","type":"Great Old One","cost":"4","combat":"0","notes":"How to Awaken The King In Yellow:1) You must have a Unit in an Area lacking a Gate2) Pay 4 Power. The King appears in that Area.Desecrate (Action: Cost 2): If the King is in an Area with no Desecration Token, roll 1 die and compare to your total units in the Area (including the King). On a roll equal or less than your unit total, place a Desecration Token in the Area. If you succeed or fail, place a Monster or Cultist with a cost of 2 or less in the Area.","text":"Cost: 4 Combat: 0
How to Awaken The King In Yellow:1) You must have a Unit in an Area lacking a Gate2) Pay 4 Power. The King appears in that Area.Desecrate (Action: Cost 2): If the King is in an Area with no Desecration Token, roll 1 die and compare to your total units in the Area (including the King). On a roll equal or less than your unit total, place a Desecration Token in the Area. If you succeed or fail, place a Monster or Cultist with a cost of 2 or less in the Area.","product":"Yellow Sign","tot":"1","img":"/factions/yellow-sign/unit-mini-king-in-yellow.png","url":"/factions/yellow-sign?units#_king-in-yellow","keywords":["unit"]},{"name":"Hastur","type":"Great Old One","cost":"10","combat":"?","notes":"How to Awaken Hastur:1) You must have a Controlled Gate and the King in Yellow in the same area.2) Pay 10 Power. Hastur appears in the King's Area.Combat: Equals the current Cost of a Ritual of Annihilation.Vengeance (Post-Battle): If Hastur is involved in a Battle, choose which Combat results are applied to which enemy Unit (e. g. apply a Kill to a particular Great Old One).","text":"Cost: 10 Combat: ?
How to Awaken Hastur:1) You must have a Controlled Gate and the King in Yellow in the same area.2) Pay 10 Power. Hastur appears in the King's Area.Combat: Equals the current Cost of a Ritual of Annihilation.Vengeance (Post-Battle): If Hastur is involved in a Battle, choose which Combat results are applied to which enemy Unit (e. g. apply a Kill to a particular Great Old One).","product":"Yellow Sign","tot":"1","img":"/factions/yellow-sign/unit-mini-hastur.png","url":"/factions/yellow-sign?units#_hastur","keywords":["unit"]},{"name":"He Who Must Not Be Named (Action: Cost 1)","type":"Spellbook","cost":"Action: Cost 1","text":"Move Hastur to any Area containing a Cultist of any Faction. You may then take a second, different Action. You may NOT take The Screaming Dead as your second Action.","product":"Yellow Sign","img":"/factions/yellow-sign/icon.png","url":"/factions/yellow-sign?spellbooks","keywords":["faction-spellbook","spellbook"]},{"name":"Passion (Ongoing)","type":"Spellbook","cost":"Ongoing","text":"When one or more of your Cultists are Eliminated by an enemy (Killed, Captured, etc.), gain 1 Power total.","product":"Yellow Sign","img":"/factions/yellow-sign/icon.png","url":"/factions/yellow-sign?spellbooks","keywords":["faction-spellbook","spellbook"]},{"name":"Shriek of the Byakhee (Action: Cost 1)","type":"Spellbook","cost":"Action: Cost 1","text":"Move any or all Byakhee from their current Area(s) to any one Area on the Map.","product":"Yellow Sign","img":"/factions/yellow-sign/icon.png","url":"/factions/yellow-sign?spellbooks","keywords":["faction-spellbook","spellbook"]},{"name":"The Screaming Dead (Action: Cost 1)","type":"Spellbook","cost":"Action: Cost 1","text":"Move the King in Yellow to an adjacent Area. Any Undead in the same Area can move with him for free. You may then take a second, different Action. You may NOT take He Who is Not to be Named as your second Action.","product":"Yellow Sign","img":"/factions/yellow-sign/icon.png","url":"/factions/yellow-sign?spellbooks","keywords":["faction-spellbook","spellbook"]},{"name":"The Third Eye (Ongoing)","type":"Spellbook","cost":"Ongoing","text":"If Hastur is in play, the cost of Desecration is reduced to 1. If the Desecration succeeds, you also get 1 Elder Sign.","product":"Yellow Sign","img":"/factions/yellow-sign/icon.png","url":"/factions/yellow-sign?spellbooks","keywords":["faction-spellbook","spellbook"]},{"name":"Zingaya (Action: Cost 1)","type":"Spellbook","cost":"Action: Cost 1","text":"If Undead are in an Area with enemy Acolyte Cultists, your enemy must Eliminate an Acolyte Cultist. Then, place an Undead in the Area","product":"Yellow Sign","img":"/factions/yellow-sign/icon.png","url":"/factions/yellow-sign?spellbooks","keywords":["faction-spellbook","spellbook"]},{"name":"Windwalker","type":"Faction","product":"Factions","img":"/factions/windwalker/icon.png","url":"/factions/windwalker","keywords":["product","faction"]},{"name":"Acolyte","type":"Cultist","cost":"1","combat":"0","notes":"Spellbook: Cannibalism","text":"Cost: 1 Combat: 0
