Hibernate (Action: Cost 0): You can perform no more Actions during the rest of this Action Phase (as if you were at 0 Power). Add your current Power to your total in the next Gather Power Phase.","product":"Rulebook Extras","tot":1,"img":"/neutral-expansions/rulebook-extras/unit-mini-ithaqua.png","url":"/neutral-expansions/rulebook-extras?units?ithaqua","keywords":["unit","neutral-unit"]},{"name":"Ferox (Ongoing)","type":"Spellbook","cost":"Ongoing","text":"Your Cultists cannot be Captured by enemy Monsters or Terrors. They are still vulnerable to enemy Great Old Ones.","product":"Rulebook Extras (Ithaqua)","img":"/neutral-expansions/rulebook-extras/unit-sil-ithaqua.svg","url":"/neutral-expansions/rulebook-extras?units?ithaqua","keywords":["spellbook","independent-spellbook"]},{"name":"Nyarlathotep","type":"Independent Great Old One","cost":"6","combat":"Equal to the total number of Spellbooks held by your enemy (Faction Spellbooks, as well as any others).","notes":"Chaos (Ongoing): Nyarlathotep can Move 2 Areas on a Move Action. He can fly over Areas containing enemy Units.","text":"Cost: 6 Combat: Equal to the total number of Spellbooks held by your enemy (Faction Spellbooks, as well as any others).
Chaos (Ongoing): Nyarlathotep can Move 2 Areas on a Move Action. He can fly over Areas containing enemy Units.","product":"Rulebook Extras","tot":1,"img":"/neutral-expansions/rulebook-extras/unit-mini-nyarlathotep.png","url":"/neutral-expansions/rulebook-extras?units?nyarlathotep","keywords":["unit","neutral-unit"]},{"name":"The Harbinger (Post-Battle)","type":"Spellbook","cost":"Post-Battle","text":"If Nyarlathotep is in a Battle in which one or more enemy Great Old Ones are Killed or Pained, receive Power equal to half of the cost of Awakening those Great Old Ones. For each enemy Great Old One so affected, you may choose to receive 2 Elder Signs instead of Power.","product":"Rulebook Extras (Nyarlathotep)","img":"/neutral-expansions/rulebook-extras/unit-sil-nyarlathotep.svg","url":"/neutral-expansions/rulebook-extras?units?nyarlathotep","keywords":["spellbook","independent-spellbook"]},{"name":"Rhan-Tegoth","type":"Independent Great Old One","cost":"4","combat":"2","notes":"Herald (Doom Phase): You never pay more than 5 Power to perform a Ritual of Annihilation, regardless of its actual cost.","text":"Cost: 4 Combat: 2
