Defilement (Action: Cost 2): If the King in Yellow is in an Area with no Desecration token, roll a die. On a roll equal to or less than the number of your Units in the Area (including the King), place a Desecration token into that Area. Whatever the result, place a Monster or Cultist with a cost of 2 or less into the Area.","product":"Rulebook Extras","tot":1,"img":"/neutral-expansions/rulebook-extras/unit-mini-the-king-in-yellow.png","url":"/neutral-expansions/rulebook-extras?units?the-king-in-yellow","keywords":["unit","neutral-unit"]},{"name":"Feast (Gather Power Phase)","type":"Spellbook","cost":"Gather Power Phase","text":"Gain 1 Power for each Area that contains a Desecration token.","product":"Rulebook Extras (The King in Yellow)","img":"/neutral-expansions/rulebook-extras/unit-sil-the-king-in-yellow.svg","url":"/neutral-expansions/rulebook-extras?units?the-king-in-yellow","keywords":["spellbook","independent-spellbook"]},{"name":"Tsathoggua","type":"Independent Great Old One","cost":"4","combat":"Equal to the number of enemy Faction Great Old Ones (not counting any Independent Great Old Ones). ","notes":"Death from Below (Doom Phase): Place the lowest-cost Monster currently in your Pool into any Area containing at least one of your Units. In the event of a tie for lowest cost, you may choose which of those Units to put into play. ","text":"Cost: 4 Combat: Equal to the number of enemy Faction Great Old Ones (not counting any Independent Great Old Ones). 
Death from Below (Doom Phase): Place the lowest-cost Monster currently in your Pool into any Area containing at least one of your Units. In the event of a tie for lowest cost, you may choose which of those Units to put into play. ","product":"Rulebook Extras","tot":1,"img":"/neutral-expansions/rulebook-extras/unit-mini-tsathoggua.png","url":"/neutral-expansions/rulebook-extras?units?tsathoggua","keywords":["unit","neutral-unit"]},{"name":"Lethargy (Action: Cost 0)","type":"Spellbook","cost":"Action: Cost 0","text":"If Tsathoggua is in play and at least one enemy player has more Power than you, do nothing. This counts as an Action.","product":"Rulebook Extras (Tsathoggua)","img":"/neutral-expansions/rulebook-extras/unit-sil-tsathoggua.svg","url":"/neutral-expansions/rulebook-extras?units?tsathoggua","keywords":["spellbook","independent-spellbook"]},{"name":"Ubbo-Sathla","type":"Independent Great Old One","cost":"4","combat":"Equal to the current position of Ubbo-Sathla’s Growth counter.","notes":"Sycophancy (Doom Phase): When an enemy player performs a Ritual of Annihilation, he chooses whether you gain 1 Doom or if he earns 1 fewer Doom.","text":"Cost: 4 Combat: Equal to the current position of Ubbo-Sathla’s Growth counter.
Sycophancy (Doom Phase): When an enemy player performs a Ritual of Annihilation, he chooses whether you gain 1 Doom or if he earns 1 fewer Doom.","product":"Rulebook Extras","tot":1,"img":"/neutral-expansions/rulebook-extras/unit-mini-ubbo-sathla.png","url":"/neutral-expansions/rulebook-extras?units?ubbo-sathla","keywords":["unit","neutral-unit"]},{"name":"Hell's Banquet (Doom Phase)","type":"Spellbook","cost":"Doom Phase","text":"Roll a die and increase Ubbo-Sathla's Growth Counter by the amount shown.","product":"Rulebook Extras (Ubbo-Sathla)","img":"/neutral-expansions/rulebook-extras/unit-sil-ubbo-sathla.svg","url":"/neutral-expansions/rulebook-extras?units?ubbo-sathla","keywords":["spellbook","independent-spellbook"]},{"name":"Yog-Sothoth","type":"Independent Great Old One","cost":"6","combat":"Equal to the number of enemy Faction Great Old Ones (not counting any Independent Great Old Ones). ","notes":"The Beyond-One (Action: Cost 1): Yog-Sothoth must be in an Area containing a Gate, but no enemy Great Old One. Move Yog-Sothoth to any Area on the Map lacking a Gate. In doing so, he takes the Gate with him, along with any Controlling Unit.","text":"Cost: 6 Combat: Equal to the number of enemy Faction Great Old Ones (not counting any Independent Great Old Ones). 
