Lord and Master (Doom Phase): When you Awaken an Independent Great Old One (except Dire Cthulhu), gain 1 Elder Sign.","product":"Kickstarter Specials","tot":1,"img":"/neutral-expansions/kickstarter-specials/unit-mini-dire-cthulhu.png","url":"/neutral-expansions/kickstarter-specials?units?dire-cthulhu","keywords":["unit","neutral-unit"]},{"name":"Non-Euclidean (Post-Battle)","type":"Spellbook","cost":"Post-Battle","text":"If Dire Cthulhu is involved in a Battle, you may assign any Battle results you inflict to any Faction with Units in the Area, even if they did not participate in the Battle. If any results are assigned to a non-participating Faction, that Faction may not use Battle abilities or Spellbooks in response. Affected Factions still select which of their units receive Battle results.","product":"Kickstarter Specials (Dire Cthulhu)","img":"/neutral-expansions/kickstarter-specials/unit-sil-dire-cthulhu.svg","url":"/neutral-expansions/kickstarter-specials?units?dire-cthulhu","keywords":["spellbook","independent-spellbook"]},{"name":"The Risen One","type":"Independent Great Old One","cost":"8","combat":"Choose any number","notes":"Reality (Ongoing): The Risen One is considered to exist in every Area in which its base overlaps. It can attack into any of them, can Move into any Area adjacent to any of them, etc. Madness (Battle):  You may roll any number of dice for the Risen One's Battle total. However, if the Risen One's side scores more Kills than its opposition, the Risen One is Eliminated.","text":"Cost: 8 Combat: Choose any number
Reality (Ongoing): The Risen One is considered to exist in every Area in which its base overlaps. It can attack into any of them, can Move into any Area adjacent to any of them, etc. Madness (Battle):  You may roll any number of dice for the Risen One's Battle total. However, if the Risen One's side scores more Kills than its opposition, the Risen One is Eliminated.","product":"Kickstarter Specials","tot":1,"img":"/neutral-expansions/kickstarter-specials/unit-mini-the-risen-one.png","url":"/neutral-expansions/kickstarter-specials?units?the-risen-one","keywords":["unit","neutral-unit"]},{"name":"Call Him (Action: Cost 1)","type":"Spellbook","cost":"Action: Cost 1","text":"Move the Risen One to any Area in which you have a Unit.","product":"Kickstarter Specials (The Risen One)","img":"/neutral-expansions/kickstarter-specials/unit-sil-the-risen-one.svg","url":"/neutral-expansions/kickstarter-specials?units?the-risen-one","keywords":["spellbook","independent-spellbook"]},{"name":"Nodens","type":"Independent Elder God","cost":"6","combat":"Add 1 Kill and 2 Pains to your Combat total (Nodens doesn't roll any Combat Dice)","notes":"Healing (Doom Phase): At the end of the Doom Phase, unless the Ritual of Annihilation track has reached Sudden Death, move the Ritual marker backwards 1 step (but not past the start).","text":"Cost: 6 Combat: Add 1 Kill and 2 Pains to your Combat total (Nodens doesn't roll any Combat Dice)
Healing (Doom Phase): At the end of the Doom Phase, unless the Ritual of Annihilation track has reached Sudden Death, move the Ritual marker backwards 1 step (but not past the start).","product":"Kickstarter Specials","tot":1,"img":"/neutral-expansions/kickstarter-specials/unit-mini-nodens.png","url":"/neutral-expansions/kickstarter-specials?units?nodens","keywords":["unit","neutral-unit"]},{"name":"Proteus (Action: Cost 2)","type":"Spellbook","cost":"Action: Cost 2","text":"Choose one of your earned Faction Spellbooks that names either a type of Unit (e.g., Acolytes or Flying Polyps). Place your Faction Glyph on that Spellbook. Nodens then benefits from that Spellbook's effects as if it were the named Unit or type of Unit.","product":"Kickstarter Specials (Nodens)","img":"/neutral-expansions/kickstarter-specials/unit-sil-nodens.svg","url":"/neutral-expansions/kickstarter-specials?units?nodens","keywords":["spellbook","independent-spellbook"]},{"name":"The Gods War Crossover","type":"Neutral Expansion","product":"Neutral Expansions","units":["Lady of Disease","Mad God","Magna Mater","Hellmother","Sun God","Thunder King"],"img":"/neutral-expansions/the-gods-war-crossover/icon.png","url":"/neutral-expansions/the-gods-war-crossover","keywords":["product","expansion"]},{"name":"Lady of Disease","type":"Independent Great Old One","cost":"2","combat":"0","notes":"Plague (Ongoing): Any player declaring Battle in the Lady of Disease Disease’s Area must pay 1 Doom (including her owner).","text":"Cost: 2 Combat: 0
